reviews.text: Your usual KFC but small restaurant and very long queue for food. Try their app if you want to avoid waiting in line.
Fast, tasty, good value, not fantastically healthy, what you'd expect from KFC!
Busy most of the time. Well located with an interesting setting.
Besides McDonald, definitely goes to KFC.
Very good place

reviews.text: 餐廳較小，一般沒有什麽特別。
很多人只是坐着嘆冷氣，無食嘢，妨礙他人
佢嗰啲鸡係多款选择，不同嘅味道有辣与唔辣有蜜糖味道，同一啲好滑嘅雪糕一齐有得食，任君选择。👍
香港既kfc應該有世界咁多kfc入面可以排前三
人多到不得了，葡撻size細到能想像！
